Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.13,0:24:40.68,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\an3\be7}辛酸痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.78,0:24:43.32,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\an3\be7}而又寂寞难耐的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.58,0:24:47.45,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\an3\be7}好想牵住你的手
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.63,0:24:51.35,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\an3\be7}无论几次我都会呼喊你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.56,0:24:55.04,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\an3\be7}即使未来无法确定
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.17,0:25:02.88,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\an3\be7}无法割舍的东西  只要想到就会心如刀绞
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.00,0:25:04.77,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\an3\be7}我就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.89,0:25:06.61,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\an3\be7}我就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.76,0:25:12.12,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\an3\be7}但是哪儿才是我的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.33,0:25:14.92,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\an3\be7}无论多久都不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.08,0:25:20.99,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\an3\be7}就留在记忆中吧 
